Definition: an elaborate practical joke in which the unsuspecting victim hunts a snipe and is typically left in the dark holding a bag and waiting for the snipe to run into it
Example: in the South a snipe hunt is practically a rite of passage
Synonyms: practical_joke, an, elaborate, practical, joke, in, which, the, unsuspecting, victim, hunts, a, snipe, and, is, typically, left, dark, holding, bag, waiting, for, to, run, into, it, South, hunt, practically, rite, of, passage
Category: noun.act
